@using Zbang.Cloudents.Mvc4WebRole.Views.Store.Resources

@model Zbang.Zbox.ViewModel.Dto.Store.ProductWithDetailDto

@*Add class big to show the bigger version of the widget*@
<div class="widget">
    <div class="lFloat banner">

    </div>
</div>

<div class="productWpr">    
    <h1>@Model.Name</h1>
    <div class="left">
        <div class="productInfoWpr">
            <table class="productPrice">
                <tr>
                    <td>@StoreResources.StudentPrice:</td>
                    <td>@Model.Price</td>
                    <td>₪</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>@StoreResources.Shipping:</td>
                    <td>@Model.DeliveryPrice</td>
                    <td>₪</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>@StoreResources.CostWithShipping:</td>
                    <td>@Model.TotalPrice</td>
                    <td>₪</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <a href="@Url.RouteUrl("StoreCheckout",new {id=Model.Id})" target="_self" class="btn3">@StoreResources.PurchaseNow</a>
            <table class="productDetails">
                <tr>
                    <td>@StoreResources.SerialNo:</td>
                    <td>@Model.CatalogNumber</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>@StoreResources.PaymentCond:</td>
                    <td>@StoreResources.UpTo @Model.NumberofPayments @StoreResources.NoInterestInstall</td>
                </tr>
                @*<tr>
                    <td>@StoreResources.Warranty:</td>
                    <td>1 year - by the official importer</td>
                </tr>*@
                <tr>
                    <td>@StoreResources.DeliveryTime:</td>
                    <td>@StoreResources.UpTo @Model.SupplyTime @StoreResources.WorkDays</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>@StoreResources.Supplier:</td>
                    <td>New Vision Digital LTD</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>@StoreResources.AdditionalInfo:</td>
                    <td>09-8989567 <small>@StoreResources.WorkHours</small></td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="right">
        <div class="imgWpr ghost">
            <img class="vCentered" alt="" src="@Model.Picture" />
        </div>
        <div class="pNameWpr">
            <h3>@Model.ExtraDetails</h3>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="pDesc">
        @Html.Raw(Model.Description)
    </div>
</div>

